<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-F9F982E9-CD95-4621-AFC8-688E5346CE82" version="1" lang="en-US"?><task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-F9F982E9-CD95-4621-AFC8-688E5346CE82" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic task)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c task oceTask-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">11 Software upgrade using the Settings Editor</title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="M148553-B105"><p class="- topic/p "> This upgrade procedure is intended for a customers in case the machine is not connected to ORS. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> If executed by customers the modification must be set in SDS and on the machine on a later moment by the service technician. Also the ADAM visit report must be created. 
</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Installation</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="GUID-96138E77-8739-417A-8191-1DC78D9208A8" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Procedure</title><table id="GUID-EA978259-36E7-4AA3-A7FC-AE1B08A4EF80" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remark 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Prepare the software packages for the upgrade with settings editor 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> 
<xref keyref="11DownloadandPrepareSoftwarewithSettingsEditor" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-90D318BD-4695-46A9-B882-323F531C80F4.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 11 Download and prepare the software package for upgrade with...?>11 Download and prepare the software package for upgrade with Settings Editor</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Use this procedure to update the software: 
</p><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="UpgradewithSettingsEditor" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-006BC600-7808-475C-A58C-76E76B752B7C.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 11 How to upgrade the system software with Settings Editor...?>11 How to upgrade the system software with Settings Editor</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check if all the system settings are still correct. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Also check that Remote Service is still working if it is used. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="ORSSETUP001" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-07BC7664-5AAE-4C27-A331-C2F6D4AB2349.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text How to set up Océ Remote Service?>How to set up On Remote Service (ORS)</xref> 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check in the specific software upgrade procedure, if additional actions are required after the software upgrade. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Create an ADAM visit for this upgrade. 
</p><note id="GUID-D877EA06-49E7-4304-ABF0-15E2EAC9591D" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">The customer is not able to create an ADAM visit. 
</p></note></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="Start_adam" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-685E6504-D43E-4063-96D4-B0A4F752A1F6.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text How to start ADAM?>How to start ADAM</xref> 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Optional: Update the RIP driver 
